node.detail_zh: 患者過往健康良好，無外遊記錄，為第 #1063 宗個案患者女兒。患者為照顧母親而一同入住檢疫中心，沒有病徵。
node.detail_en: The patient has good past health and no recent travel history. She is the daughter of patient #1063. She was admitted to the quarantine centre to take care of her mother. She has no symptoms.
node.classification_zh: 輸入個案的密切接觸者
